										"type": "text",
										"text": "class Solution {"

							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "  Deque<String> Stack = new ArrayDeque<>();"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "  Set<String> ops = new HashSet<>(List.of(\"+\", \"-\", \"*\", \"/\"));"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "hardBreak"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "  public int evalRPN(String[] tokens) {"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "    int n = tokens.length;"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "    helper(tokens, n, 0);"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "    int res = Integer.parseInt(Stack.pollLast());"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "    return res;"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",

								]

							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "  void helper(String[] arr, int len, int i){"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "    if(i>=len)return;"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "    if(ops.contains(arr[i])){"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "      System.out.println(arr[i] + \" is an op \");"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "      int y = Integer.parseInt(Stack.pollLast());"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "      int x = Integer.parseInt(Stack.pollLast());"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "      int acc=0;"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "      if(arr[i] == \"+\") acc = x+y;"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "      else if(arr[i] == \"-\") acc = x-y;"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "      else if(arr[i] == \"*\") acc = x*y;"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "      else if(arr[i] == \"/\") acc = x/y;"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},
								"content": [
									{
										"type": "text",
										"text": "      Stack.offerLast(String.valueOf(acc));"
									}
								]
							},
							{
								"type": "paragraph",
								"attrs": {
									"dir": "auto"
								},

									{

									{

										"text": "    else{"
